# ─── Optional: NASA API key ───────────────────────────────────────────
# The "Astronomy picture of the day" card uses NASA's APOD API. Without a
# key it falls back to DEMO_KEY, which is shared and rate-limited (429s).
#
# Get a free key in ~30 seconds at https://api.nasa.gov, then either:
#   • copy this file to `.env` and paste the key below (local dev), or
#   • set VITE_NASA_API_KEY in your Cloudflare Workers Build environment
#     variables and redeploy.
# Vite bakes VITE_-prefixed vars in at build time.
VITE_NASA_API_KEY=DEMO_KEY
